I think you are missing the point on this though... AA's were somewhat new when PoP was released, AA's were much harder to get, and most of the people I knew that didn't play 24-7 were still baron/ness or possibly working on their level 55 AA's.  DC was difficult to get back then.  To release a whole new expansion with not a single DCable mob in it for these classes would cause considerable uproar and people demanding refund of AA's due to the effort put in before PoP experience was available.  They were a bit liberal on putting something DCable for most able classes in just about every zone, though not always easy to find or get to, but I don't think it really had to do with soloability.
