Great point <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Look at it this way, who is more social?
<br />

<br />
Player A: Runs off to a faraway corner of the world and kills mobs by themselves. They join several chat channels, participate in guild chat, are sending /tells, etc.
<br />

<br />
Player B: Joins a group, with a steady stream of mobs coming in, decides to drop out of chat and sends guild text to a hidden window so they don't get distracted.
<br />

<br />
